TAG TEAM LEAGUE

TEAM PURPLE

Amber Rayne & Brix
Combined HT: 127"
Combined WT: 235lbs
Record: (1-0)

TEAM BLACK

Adrianna & Devi
Combined HT:128"
Combined WT: 244lbs
Record:(0-0)

Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's third league match.
Team Purple vs, Team Black. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.

The rules are set: (1) Three tags per team, per round.
(2) Three 12-minute non-scripted wrestling rounds. (3)
Last round consists of the winners tying up,
dominating, humiliating, and brutally fucking the
losers.

Team Purple: Won their first match vs Red, and are currently the only undefeated Tag Team. However, tragedy struck, Von Tess was injured and will be out for 1 or 2 months. In her place steps in Brix, a very skilled and talented replacement.

Team Black: This is Team Black's first match. They have size and speed. Both are extremely competitive, and hate to lose. Devi has more experience but Adrianna has strength and size.

This is the third match in a row that a winner was decided in the last minute of the match. That is how closely the Tag Team league is matching up.
title: TAG TEAM LEAGUE
